HEADWORD: Bulbar
<hw>Bulb"ar</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Of or pertaining to
bulb; especially, in medicine, pertaining to the bulb of the spinal
cord, or <xex>medulla oblongata</xex>; <as>as, <ex>bulbar</ex>
paralysis</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Bulbed</ent>⟦br⟧
